<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Fitness Brand</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #090909;
      color: white;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .navbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.82);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 16px 0;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .brand {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #cfcfcf;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    header {
      padding: 90px 0 70px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517836357463-d25dfeac3438?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80") center/cover no-repeat;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 34px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: #d3d3d3;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.7rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: #d0d0d0;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .button-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .primary {
      background: white;
      color: black;
    }

    .secondary {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
      color: white;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(140px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .stat-box {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    .stat-box strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .stat-box span {
      color: #bcbcbc;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 72px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }

    .section-subtext {
      color: #b8b8b8;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
    }

    .about-grid,
    .grid-3,
    .gallery-grid,
    .testimonial-grid,
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .grid-3,
    .testimonial-grid,
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .card {
      background: #111;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #222;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card p,
    .card li {
      color: #bcbcbc;
    }

    .feature-list {
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin: 16px 0 0;
    }

    .feature-list li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .about-image,
    .gallery-card img {
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      object-fit: cover;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .about-image {
      min-height: 420px;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .gallery-card {
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #111;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #222;
    }

    .gallery-card img {
      height: 280px;
    }

    .gallery-card .caption {
      padding: 16px 18px 18px;
    }

    .gallery-card .caption h4 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }

    .quote {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .quote-name {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
    }

    .social-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .social-pill {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #151515;
      border: 1px solid #262626;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #dedede;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .social-pill:hover {
      color: white;
      border-color: #3a3a3a;
    }

    .cta {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #111, #181818);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 78px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #222;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    }

    .cta h2 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .cta p {
      color: #bdbdbd;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px 20px 40px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #777;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero,
      .about-grid,
      .grid-3,
      .gallery-grid,
      .testimonial-grid,
      .contact-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      header {
        padding: 70px 0 55px;
      }

      .hero-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .nav-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .container {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 26px));
      }

      .hero-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .button-row {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <div class="brand">BD Fitness</div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#results">Results</a>
        <a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <div class="container hero">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Online Coaching • Content • Transformation</span>
        <h1>Build your physique and your brand.</h1>
        <p>
          A stronger website for a fitness creator, coach, or athlete. Showcase your training style,
          your results, your content, and your offers in one clean place.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn primary">Start Coaching</a>
          <a href="#results" class="btn secondary">View Results</a>
        </div>
        <div class="social-row">
          <a class="social-pill" href="#">Instagram</a>
          <a class="social-pill" href="#">YouTube</a>
          <a class="social-pill" href="#">TikTok</a>
          <a class="social-pill" href="mailto:yourname@email.com">Email</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <strong>1:1</strong>
          <span>Customized coaching plans</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <strong>Macros</strong>
          <span>Nutrition targets and adjustments</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <strong>Content</strong>
          <span>Fitness creator positioning</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <strong>Results</strong>
          <span>Built around consistency and progression</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div>
        <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
        <p class="section-subtext">
          I help lifters build muscle, lose fat, and improve how they present themselves online.
          This site is built to make your personal brand look more serious and more complete.
        </p>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>What this site now includes</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Large hero section with a background image</li>
            <li>About section with visual layout</li>
            <li>Services cards for coaching and content</li>
            <li>Gallery section for physique or content photos</li>
            <li>Testimonials for social proof</li>
            <li>Contact section and stronger call to action</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img
          class="about-image"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583454110551-21f2fa2afe61?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Athlete training in a gym"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
      <p class="section-subtext">
        Use these cards to explain what you offer. You can later change the text to match your exact coaching or content services.
      </p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Training Plans</h3>
          <p>Structured lifting programs built around progression, recovery, execution, and intensity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Nutrition Guidance</h3>
          <p>Macros, cardio structure, meal ideas, and adjustment strategies for cutting or growing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Content Growth</h3>
          <p>Position your page better with fitness branding, posting ideas, and cleaner conversion paths.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="results">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Results & Content</h2>
      <p class="section-subtext">
        These image blocks make the page feel much more real. Replace them with your own physique updates, client transformations, gym shots, or content screenshots.
      </p>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534438327276-14e5300c3a48?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Gym physique and training photo" />
          <div class="caption">
            <h4>Transformation Focus</h4>
            <p>Show before and after photos, weight changes, or prep updates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518611012118-696072aa579a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Fitness creator filming workout content" />
          <div class="caption">
            <h4>Creator Content</h4>
            <p>Highlight your reels, training clips, daily vlogs, or exercise demos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019614242-c5c5dee9f50b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Athlete working with coaching client" />
          <div class="caption">
            <h4>Coaching Experience</h4>
            <p>Use this space to show check-ins, client wins, or your training environment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Testimonials</h2>
      <p class="section-subtext">
        Social proof helps a lot. These can be client quotes, comments from followers, or transformation reviews.
      </p>
      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <p class="quote">“The plan was simple to follow, intense enough to work, and easy to fit around my schedule. I looked noticeably leaner in a few weeks.”</p>
          <div class="quote-name">Client One</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="quote">“The website and content flow instantly made the brand look more legit. It feels like an actual coaching business now.”</p>
          <div class="quote-name">Creator Review</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="quote">“Macros, cardio, and training were all laid out clearly. I didn’t have to guess what to do next.”</p>
          <div class="quote-name">Client Two</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
      <p class="section-subtext">
        Add your real links here. Right now these are placeholders so you can publish the site immediately and swap them out after.
      </p>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Instagram</h3>
          <p>@yourhandle</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn secondary">Open Instagram</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>YouTube</h3>
          <p>Your channel or weekly series</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn secondary">Watch Videos</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Email</h3>
          <p>yourname@email.com</p>
          <a href="mailto:yourname@email.com" class="btn secondary">Send Email</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to turn this into a real brand site?</h2>
      <p>
        Replace the placeholder text, swap in your own photos, and connect your real socials. Once you upload this as index.html, you can publish it directly through GitHub Pages.
      </p>
      <div class="button-row" style="justify-content:center;">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="#about" class="btn secondary">Edit My Info</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 BD Fitness. Built for GitHub Pages.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

